I finally found a clothing line that is geared toward middle age instead of young girls."}, {"review_3"=>"This style of Alfred Dunner tops is always comfortable to wear whether it is a cotton type like this one, or a polyester top to wear as business casual to work."}, {"review_4"=>"Very good quality! description: Bold and chic, this shirred one-piece swimsuit will complement your curves and have you beach-ready in no time. tank straps built-in soft cups tummy control partially lined nylon/elastane hand wash, line dry imported
Reviews: {"review"=>[{"review_1"=>"Anything NOT black is always a welcome sight when I'm shopping for suits. I bought this suit to wear in the jacuzzi at the gym. Since there always seems to be more men than women there, I looked for a suit with maximum coverage -- at my age and as a married lady, I don't want to look like I'm trying too hard."}, {"review_2"=>"I've always appreciated the quality that Maxine of Hollywood suits have consistently delivered. Overall, a conservative but figure flattering design."}, {"review_3"=>"When the suit arrived, I was pleasantly surprised that the pretty paisley print fabric is much more rich and exotic than it looks in the photo; the description says \"black\" but this is definitely more on the burgundy/maroon side."}, {"review_4"=>"I really like this suit, fit etc. However the deep colors that were represented are not how the suit looked. I returned it and bought a black and white. Very pretty.I ordered this online with a coupon. I do feel the coupon should have applied on the 2nd order as well."}, {"review_5"=>"I usually don't feel confident in a bathing suit but this one did well to hide the extra weight I carry in my midsection. Helps to hold it in and gives a nice shape. Also very comfortable and good quality material. It has a gathered seam that goes down the front to give it a little bit of unique style. It's not just a plain grandma-like one piece, it's really cute."}, {"review_6"=>"First, I like the cut of the legs -- the high-cut type are not for me. Secondly, the neckline works for me so I do not have to buy a special mastectomy swimsuit. The suit is well-made & helps flatten my stomach. I have bought this before in black, and it is great!"}, {"review_7"=>"I love this style---the legs go all the way down my hips, covering my \"saddle bags\". Without this my only alternative was a skirted suit."}, {"review_8"=>"Very pleased with modest style and the fit. The black is more marroon than black whichI like also. Great value for the sale priceI I paid."}, {"review_9"=>"finally found a bathing suit that fit me and doesn't skimp on the places you need the most. I love it and I am coming back to buy another one. Thanks"}, {"review_10"=>"I am 5'3\", 145 lbs, and wear a size 10 pant. I bought a size 12 swimsuit and it fits perfectly. The straps are thick for chest support, small fabric creases for flattering the mommy tummy, and it sits just above the thighs for good bottom coverage. Best of all, the neck is higher cut so \"the girls\" are not making a debut. I love the vibrant colors, fast shipping, and am very pleased with my purchase."}]}

description: The vibrant print and flattering styling of our v-neck swimdress will keep you feeling confident and comfortable throughout the season. soft cups partially lined nylon/LYCRA® spandex hand wash, line dry imported
Reviews: {"review"=>[{"review_1"=>"As a woman of a certain age and weight, I've always been discouraged in the hunt for a swimsuit that I wouldn't hate being seen in! The price was so reasonable that I figured if I hated the suit, I could still keep it around for an emergency swim with my non-judgmental grandchildren. It fit extremely well, possibly even could have gone a size smaller, but it really did fit great! Not only that -- It looked GOOD! Even in front of a full length mirror! Reviews: {"review"=>[{"review_1"=>"Love it! Looks great!
